          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Will Core One Pro fit my ears?",
            "answer": "<p>Even better — Core One Pro was refined using data from over 1,000 ear canal scans to ensure an even more secure and comfortable fit. And we offer a 60-day risk-free trial, even without return fees.</p>",
            "opened": true
          }
        },
        "accordion_hMirnY": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I wear Core One Pro all day?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, it’s designed to be featherlight and ultra-comfortable for extended use, with improved sweat and dust resistance.</p>",
            "opened": false
          }
        },
        "accordion_BMbFKn": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What if the product doesn’t work for me?",
            "answer": "<p>No worries — we offer a 60-day risk-free return policy. Try it in your daily life, and if you're not satisfied, simply return it.</p>",
            "opened": false
          }
        },
        "accordion_dUtLyU": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is there a warranty?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, Core One Pro comes with an <strong>18-month limited warranty</strong>, including <strong>12 months of standard coverage plus an additional 6 months free during the launch period</strong>. This extended warranty provides peace of mind while you enjoy your hearing aids.</p>",
            "opened": false
          }
        },
        "accordion_XkXY9E": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How can I get support?",
            "answer": "<p>Our hearing support team is available Monday through Friday, from 9:00 AM to 6:00 PM (PST), via email at support@ceretone.com or by phone at (866) 283-4262.</p>",
            "opened": false
          }
        },
        "accordion_efbwMW": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is the tinnitus masking feature, and how do I use it?",
            "answer": "<p>The tinnitus masking feature generates calming background sounds (like white noise or ocean waves) to cover ringing/buzzing in your ears.</p><p>To activate it:</p><ul><li>Double-tap your hearing aid twice quickly to cycle through programs until masking starts.</li><li>Or long-press (3 seconds) the charging case button while the device is inside.</li></ul>",
            "opened": false
          }
        },
        "accordion_Xd6HQ7": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How is Core One Pro different from Core One?",
            "answer": "<p>Core One Pro offers stronger sound output, 160% better noise reduction, and two additional sound modes — including wind noise management and tinnitus masking — all while staying just as discreet.</p>",
            "opened": false
          }
        }
